    "gp_section_559588505756435576": {
      "type": "gp-section-559588505756435576",
      "settings": {
        "section_preload": "false",
        "checksum": "0cb6ce6d32be662cf9a86680d3bbe38e7ad9e9b60b5f880af5d2c207115b2276_1_1_1_0__1",
        "ggY1FOBTJPT_text": "If You Want to Relieve Hip and Lower Back Pain… It Starts With How You Sleep",
        "ggRHvYz4lwz_text": "<p>Did you know that misalignment of the spine during sleep can lead to pinched nerves, stiff painful joints, and restless nights?</p><p> </p><p><strong>Lack of proper lower body support while side sleeping pulls your hips and spine out of the natural alignment,</strong> which puts pressure on your joints and muscles, and reduces space around your nerves.</p><p> </p><p>As the space narrows, <strong>spinal discs start to press against the sciatic nerve</strong>, leading to compression and irritation. <strong>When this nerve gets compressed, you experience agonizing, searing pain</strong> that travels the entire length of the nerve, also known as Sciatica.</p><p> </p><p>Now imagine that every single night when we sleep unsupported for hours...</p><p> </p><p>The <strong>negative impact of misalignment and pressure gets worse as we grow older,</strong> because the protective cushioning between the spinal discs and joints thins out.</p><p> </p><p>This is the root cause of hip and back pain for side sleepers and the leading reason why most struggle with Sciatica.</p>",
        "ggyYdmZNRiY_youtubeUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M",
        "ggyYdmZNRiY_vimeoUrl": "https://vimeo.com/347119375",
        "ggyYdmZNRiY_html5Url": "https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/b713d74658714c5e8ed09044c63f273a.mp4",
        "ggk3P9DD54t_text": "The SmoothSpine Alignment Pillow Aligns Your Spine And Releases Pressure on the Nerves And Joints",
        "ggA8eGoMQXA_text": "<p>When you place the SmoothSpine Alignment Pillow between your legs, <strong>it helps keep your hips and your spine in a neutral, straight alignment.</strong></p><p> </p><p>The comfortably firm memory foam is designed to fit perfectly between your legs, giving you the ideal amount of support,preventing twisting and pulling.</p><p> </p><p>This support gently stabilizes your lower body and spine, which <strong>reduces pressure on your joints, muscles, and nerves.</strong></p><p> </p><p>Normally, you would need to spend hours a week exercising to correct the misalignment, but with the SmoothSpine Alignment Pillow, it happens effortlessly while you sleep.</p><p> </p><p>As your body stays supported throughout the night, <strong>you will experience pain-free sleep, wake up feeling more refreshed, and move significantly easier during daily life.</strong></p>",
        "ggKK5_keTdl_youtubeUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M",
        "ggKK5_keTdl_vimeoUrl": "https://vimeo.com/347119375",
        "ggKK5_keTdl_html5Url": "https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/612b7c6ccce2485888ad0a7334313cce.mp4",
        "ggqTbuULINK_youtubeUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M",
        "ggqTbuULINK_vimeoUrl": "https://vimeo.com/347119375",
        "ggqTbuULINK_html5Url": "https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/612b7c6ccce2485888ad0a7334313cce.mp4"
      }
    },
    "gp_section_559588505756501112": {
      "type": "gp-section-559588505756501112",
      "settings": {
        "section_preload": "false",
        "checksum": "a58cab9fd4260a6fb6fc84bd8f831fd959e69f65c7839f1fc42562525dcea53e_1_1_1_0__1",
        "ggH4_VfuWtt_text": "Over 57,000+ Side-Sleepers Are Using the SmoothSpine Alignment Pillow to Sleep Pain-Free",
        "ggRrP-62Kic_text": "<p>The SmoothSpine Alignment Pillow has become a <strong>nationwide favorite!</strong></p><p> </p><p>Countless people reported massive improvements after just a few nights with the pillow! And almost everyone continues using it every night.</p><p> </p><p>Within a few nights of using the <strong>SmoothSpine Alignment Pillow,</strong> you can expect to start noticing reduced discomfort and better sleep.</p>",
        "ggoskO8o_bu_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-97042735-715a-4957-901b-946ce11e026d.svg",
        "gg0qe2SLfDv_text": "<p><strong>No more sleepless nights trying to find a pain-free position.</strong></p>",
        "ggA4-5kuFNx_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-97042735-715a-4957-901b-946ce11e026d.svg",
        "gglZ0gcwAvm_text": "<p><strong>No more waking up with painful hips or a sore back.</strong></p>",
        "ggmqBzP3i-R_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-97042735-715a-4957-901b-946ce11e026d.svg",
        "ggrVkrkcFqn_text": "<p><strong>No more discomfort that keeps you from enjoying your life.</strong></p>",
        "ggxP0uka1UT_text": "<p>Just place the SmoothSpine Alignment Pillow between your legs, get comfortable, and enjoy all the benefits of a normal life.</p><p> </p><p>Plus, the elastic strap is uniquely designed to fit all leg sizes no matter your thigh circumference</p>",
        "gg6pJSKK3N9_youtubeUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M",
        "gg6pJSKK3N9_vimeoUrl": "https://vimeo.com/347119375",
        "gg6pJSKK3N9_html5Url": "https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/a9f1bc5f8f054756b131215b9152d024.mp4",
        "ggfj4F0mUQq_text": "Professionally Designed &amp; Recommended",
        "ggLW093RZa7_text": "<p>Tried, Tested, and Endorsed: Physical therapists, chiropractors, and physiotherapists recommend <strong>the SmoothSpine Alignment Pillow</strong> to their clients.</p><p> </p><p>And <strong>the feedback has been incredible!</strong> Many reported significantly less joint and muscle pain, meaning healthier hips, back, and legs. The result? Better sleep, reduced stress, and no pain.</p><p> </p><p>What sets the SmoothSpine Alignment Pillow apart? The innovative design, unique premium materials, and soft elastic strap that keeps the pillow in place even as you toss and turn.</p><p> </p><p>For <strong>a fraction of what you would spend on conventional therapy,</strong> the SmoothSpine Alignment Pillow offers long-lasting relief, and a professional level of care.</p><p> </p><p>It’s a one-time affordable investment in your (sleep) health that you simply cannot ignore.</p>",
        "ggK5-kgHF6T_youtubeUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M",
        "ggK5-kgHF6T_vimeoUrl": "https://vimeo.com/347119375",
        "ggK5-kgHF6T_html5Url": "https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/1d566132d8a94c4891ac85a5702f66e7.mp4",
        "gg_-pF50g9y_youtubeUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M",
        "gg_-pF50g9y_vimeoUrl": "https://vimeo.com/347119375",
        "gg_-pF50g9y_html5Url": "https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/1d566132d8a94c4891ac85a5702f66e7.mp4",
        "ggzZ-A2Csf9_text": "Don’t Just Take Our Word for It… Try It for 90 Nights Risk-Free",
        "ggnbFRB_HFB_text": "<p>Order your SmoothSpine Alignment Pillow today… Use it for up to 3 full months… And then <strong>decide based on the results if you want to keep it or not anytime during the 90-night period.</strong></p><p> </p><p>If you’re not happy with the results, feel like it hasn’t improved your sleep, or did not help relieve pain, we’ll give you a full refund – no questions asked.</p><p> </p><p>So it either <strong>helps you sleep better and relieve pain in your hips, back and legs like advertised,</strong> or you get your money back the same day.</p><p> </p><p>That’s how confident we are in the SmoothSpine Alignment Pillow.</p>",
        "ggK6P-UYQ7X_label": "<p>GET UP TO 52% OFF TODAY ONLY! 👉</p>",
        "ggTJiycYfKs_youtubeUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M",
        "ggTJiycYfKs_vimeoUrl": "https://vimeo.com/347119375",
        "ggTJiycYfKs_html5Url": "https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/42f87d03787b45d888c6df8d4109c5d9.mp4"
      }
    },
